  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">This information is used to measure the number of visitors to the various sections of our site and identify system performance or problem areas We also use this information to help us develop the site analyze patterns of usage and to make the site more useful This information is not used for associating search terms or patterns of site navigation with individual users USA gov may anonymize and provide this information to third party entities for the purposes of research analysis We do not share or sell visitor data for the purposes of advertising marketing or any other commercial purpose</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

